author: Leila Ettachfini, Michelle Garcia, Kate Lowenstein
title: Gaza Was ‘An Emergency Even Before Corona.' What Happens Now?
description: Dr. Salam Khashan, an OB-GYN in Gaza, on what it's like to brace for COVID-19 in a place already suffering from severe medical shortages.
content:
Salam Khashans shifts at the Nasser Medical Complex in Gaza can exceed 24 hours.
